00:45:47.530 --> 00:45:48.530
&gt;&gt;Paul: Yep.

00:45:48.530 --> 00:45:50.720
&gt;&gt;audience male #10: É would you say that
worked out well? Was that a good idea if you

00:45:50.720 --> 00:45:55.740
were Ronald Reagan in 1982 or whatever? Or
