00:48:49.069 --> 00:48:54.859
from happening again, but we can make it so
painful that we can encourage people to act

00:48:54.859 --> 00:49:00.289
responsibly. In the end, to have everyone
act responsibly all the time is a pretty tough

00:49:00.289 --> 00:49:01.289
order.

00:49:01.289 --> 00:49:02.289
[Paul laughs]

